      <title>布兰森投资的热气球旅游公司因现金短缺裁员</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/branson-backed-balloon-tourism-firm-cuts-staff-as-cash-drains</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Space Perspective 是一家由理查德·布兰森 (Richard Branson) 投资的初创公司，旨在利用热气球将游客送至平流层。去年年底，由于资金短缺，该公司几乎解雇了所有员工。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/branson-backed-balloon-tourism-firm-cuts-staff-as-cash-drains</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 22 Jan 2025 18:14:09 GMT</pubDate>
