    <item>
      <title>谷歌赢得英国裁决 阻止俄罗斯罚款金额超过全球 GDP</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/google-wins-uk-ruling-blocking-russian-fine-worth-more-than-world-gdp</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Alphabet Inc. 旗下的谷歌赢得英国法院的一项裁决，阻止俄罗斯媒体公司扣押该科技巨头的全球资产，以追讨俄罗斯法院判处的罚款，这些罚款所产生的利息已相当于世界经济总和的数倍。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/google-wins-uk-ruling-blocking-russian-fine-worth-more-than-world-gdp</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 22 Jan 2025 17:02:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
